will ever happen and without order). Some of this points will be part of the
upcoming @{b}WolfPac 2@{ub}, which will be more like a complete new game than just
another version of "this" WolfPac.

* more levels, graphics and sounds

* Joystick support

* AHI support

* a "real" ceiling for some levels

* scores and highscores

* a leveleditor

* extras (others than the superpill)

* different kinds of Ghosts etc.

* speedup of everything :)

